Clipboard variable supports Clipboard history in Windows 10 version 1809 and later.
Clipboard history must be enabled in Windows Settings → Clipboard.

Current clipboard item: <atext contenteditable="false" type="clipboard">📋</atext>
1st previous clipboard item: <atext contenteditable="false" type="clipboard" history="1">📋⟲1</atext>
2nd previous clipboard item: <atext contenteditable="false" type="clipboard" history="2">📋⟲2</atext>
